item.title: By: Erin-Kurley
item.dc:creator: Erin-Kurley
item.description: I bought one of these lipsticks and I totally get why you'd want to have a million of them! There are SO MANY!! So hard to choose. But luckily I chose one that makes me want to stare at myself all day.
